We missed the food because we got here at 1.15am.  The place is open from 1pm to 1am and kitchen closes at 12am.  So just writing so that no one else misses the place because of the incorrect times.  Place is cute and the bartender gave us free drinks because we missed the kitchen and walked a long way to check out the place.Update after we ate:  food was okay.  Asparagus was great especially with the sauce.  Shrimp and sun dried tomatoes were okay. Tandoori chicken wings were good.
